This repository contains an implementation of a Conical ULX model in python.

For more information see:
  https://arxiv.org/pdf/1612.05035.pdf
  https://arxiv.org/pdf/1705.06488.pdf

Requirements
------------
Shapely : https://pypi.org/project/Shapely/

Current Features
----------------
- 3D Implementation of conical geometry

Planned Features
----------------
- Photon scattering